Thirty thousand!

362
00:30:24,625 --> 00:30:27,290
Forty thousand!

363
00:30:27,375 --> 00:30:29,957
Lala bhai, sixty thousand!

364
00:30:30,083 --> 00:30:31,540
Sixty thousand!
Sixty thousand, once...

365
