Is this a joke, Gaitonde?

545
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:05,207
I'm sorry but this is his
only official photograph...

546
00:42:05,291 --> 00:42:06,415
in the police records.

547
00:42:06,625 --> 00:42:07,749
Vijay Chauhan.

548
00:42:08,750 --> 00:42:10,957
