Move it. Madhuri Dixit, right!

581
00:45:30,583 --> 00:45:33,415
She is my darling Kaali.

582
00:45:33,833 --> 00:45:36,082
You look so much like Silk Smita...

583
00:45:36,166 --> 00:45:37,582
Silk Smita!

584
