Oh my Kaali!

585
00:45:39,666 --> 00:45:41,207
Why are you talking about her, Laxmi?

586
00:45:41,333 --> 00:45:42,457
I'm happy to be Kaali.

587
00:45:42,541 --> 00:45:43,665
Kaali Gawde.

588
00:45:43,750 --> 00:45:44,874
Take a look at my staff.

589
