644
00:48:55,416 --> 00:48:56,540
Nothing.

645
00:49:05,333 --> 00:49:06,582
I'm sorry, Viju.

646
00:49:07,916 --> 00:49:09,040
Sorry.

647
00:49:10,916 --> 00:49:12,290
I said too much.

648
00:49:19,250 --> 00:49:20,499
I remember everything...

649
00:49:22,125 --> 00:49:23,374
I understand everything.

