00:49:31,541 --> 00:49:32,665
what can I do?

652
00:49:35,583 --> 00:49:37,665
Sometimes,
unknowingly I end up dreaming.

653
00:49:47,416 --> 00:49:48,749
But don't worry about me.

654
00:49:51,666 --> 00:49:52,790
I'm fine, just the way I am.

