765
01:01:07,875 --> 01:01:08,957
Get him to stop.

766
01:01:10,000 --> 01:01:11,374
Nothing... nothing Azhar.

767
01:01:11,500 --> 01:01:12,624
Idiot!

768
01:01:15,000 --> 01:01:16,749
Borkar, that bastard!

769
01:01:17,000 --> 01:01:18,207
Kancha's slave.

770
